data.description: Classic ranch home with 3 bedrooms and a full bath on the main floor.  Mid Century modern character with some updates.  Three living rooms for maximum livability.  Basement has a living room with a wood fire place, a bar and a game room with a pool table and all of the accessories included.  A fully updated bathroom in basement and a large laundry room with a workshop area.  The backyard has a nice size deck with pergola and porch swing all under a great big tree.  Fire pit and small garden area with a wooden shed as well.  Book a showing asap for this great house.
